--- WAIT FAILPOINT variants ---
SYSTEM WAIT FAILPOINT fp
SYSTEM WAIT FAILPOINT fp PAUSE
SYSTEM WAIT FAILPOINT fp RESUME
--- VIEW management (REFRESH / START / STOP / CANCEL / WAIT / REPLICATED) ---
SYSTEM REFRESH VIEW db.v
SYSTEM START REPLICATED VIEW db.v
SYSTEM STOP REPLICATED VIEW db.v
SYSTEM CANCEL VIEW db.v
SYSTEM WAIT VIEW db.v
--- TEST VIEW (SET / UNSET FAKE TIME) ---
SYSTEM TEST VIEW db.v SET FAKE TIME \'2023-01-01 00:00:00\'
SYSTEM TEST VIEW db.v UNSET FAKE TIME
--- ALLOCATE MEMORY ---
SYSTEM ALLOCATE MEMORY 1024
SYSTEM ALLOCATE MEMORY 1048576
--- FLUSH LOGS with multiple log tables ---
SYSTEM FLUSH LOGS query_log, part_log
SYSTEM FLUSH ASYNC INSERT QUEUE db.t1, db.t2
--- RELOAD DELTA KERNEL TRACING ---
SYSTEM RELOAD DELTA KERNEL TRACING WARN
SYSTEM RELOAD DELTA KERNEL TRACING DEBUG
--- RELOAD MODEL(S) ---
SYSTEM RELOAD MODEL my_model
SYSTEM RELOAD MODELS
--- LISTEN protocol variants ---
SYSTEM START LISTEN HTTP
SYSTEM START LISTEN HTTPS
SYSTEM START LISTEN TCP SECURE
SYSTEM START LISTEN TCP WITH PROXY
SYSTEM START LISTEN INTERSERVER HTTP
SYSTEM START LISTEN INTERSERVER HTTPS
SYSTEM START LISTEN MYSQL
SYSTEM START LISTEN POSTGRESQL
SYSTEM START LISTEN GRPC
SYSTEM START LISTEN PROMETHEUS
SYSTEM START LISTEN QUERIES DEFAULT
SYSTEM START LISTEN QUERIES CUSTOM
SYSTEM STOP LISTEN HTTP
--- FILESYSTEM CACHE with path / key ---
SYSTEM CLEAR FILESYSTEM CACHE \'my_cache\'
SYSTEM CLEAR FILESYSTEM CACHE \'my_cache\' KEY xyz
--- QUERY CACHE with tag ---
SYSTEM CLEAR QUERY CACHE TAG \'mytag\'
--- SUSPEND / KILL / SHUTDOWN ---
SYSTEM SUSPEND FOR 1 SECOND
SYSTEM KILL
SYSTEM SHUTDOWN
